{
  "chapter": 45,
  "chapter_summary": "第四十五回 又是金手\n\n小方和阳光在客栈中发现一只金手从阳光的包袱中掉落，此金手正是吕三号令群豪的信物。两人由此推断班察巴那可能并未骗过吕三，他们的行踪早已暴露。阳光怀疑隔壁的赵胡氏趁同车之便将金手塞入包袱。夜间两人跟踪赵胡氏到厨房，发现她脸手皮肤粗糙如橘皮，身体却雪白如新，显然是用药易容改扮。小方和阳光判断赵群夫妻是吕三派来的杀手，决定静观其变。次日商队进入险峻山区，他们乘坐的车轴被人锯断，车厢倾覆。小方踢开车厢，发现埋伏在其中的父子杀手已中毒身亡，死前手持暗器筒却未能出手。金手的出现和杀手的离奇死亡，暗示着更复杂的阴谋正在展开。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你看看床下面是不是有样东西？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "text": "这包袱真的是你今天早上亲手包好的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "绝对是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "text": "那时候这只金手在不在这个包袱里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "不在。绝对不在。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "text": "刚才你真的亲眼看见它是从包袱里掉下来的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我看得很清楚。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "text": "那么这只金手是怎么会到你包袱里去的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我不知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "text": "今天有谁碰过这个包袱？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "没有。好像没有。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "text": "是好像没有？还是绝对没有？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "text": "有没有人能够找个机会把这只金手塞到你包袱里去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "有。只有一个人。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "text": "谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "就是那个吵得我们整夜睡不着的女人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "text": "也许班察巴那根本就没有骗过吕三，我们的行踪早已被发现。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "所以他早就派出人来跟踪我们。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "text": "你认为那对夫妻就是吕三派来的人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我早就对他们有点疑心了，一个正正经经的良家妇女，明明知道隔壁有人，晚上怎么会像那样鬼叫？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "也许根本就是故意要吵得我们睡不着，让我们白天没精神，她才有机会下手。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "text": "如果吕三真的已经查出我们的行踪，为什么不索性杀了我们。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "text": "因为他还想从我们身上找出卜鹰的下落，所以只有派人在暗中跟踪，而且绝不能让我们发现。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "text": "如果那对夫妻真是吕三派来暗中跟踪我们的，为什么又把一只金手塞在我们的包袱里？他们这么做岂非也暴露了自己的身份？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "text": "我去看看。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "我也去。这次你可不能再把我一个人留在屋里。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你看见了没有？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "text": "看见了什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你自己应该知道看见了什么？你看得比我清楚得多。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "text": "嗯！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你看她脸上和手上的皮肤像什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "text": "像橘子皮。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "她身上的皮肤呢？她身上的皮肤简直就像是假的，像羊奶，我从来也没有看过皮肤像她这么好的女人。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你有没有见过这样的女人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "text": "没有，除非……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "除非她也跟我一样，也用一种像‘光阴树汁’那样的药物，把自己的脸和手都改变了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "现在我们应该怎么办？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "text": "我也不知道。看样子我们好像只有装糊涂，只有等。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "等什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "text": "等着看他们的动静，等他们自己先沉不住气，等机会出手。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "你去看看，看看是怎么回事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 259,
      "line_end": 259
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "text": "来了。总算来了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 267,
      "line_end": 267
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "是他们？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 269,
      "line_end": 269
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": "char_yang_guang",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 271,
      "line_end": 271
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yang_guang",
      "speaker_name": "阳光",
      "listener": "char_xiao_fang",
      "text": "不管怎么样，他们总算没有让我们等得太久。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 273,
      "line_end": 273
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "两位为什么还不出来？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 279,
      "line_end": 279
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "小方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "两位为什么还不出手？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 281,
      "line_end": 281
    }
